{"tid":2109550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際法庭裁「九段線」違法","createTime":"2020-07-15T09:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T15:03:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":337,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"07d12bf3cce421b6a2886254133051eea2f9e07b","tid":2109550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/EHODDM5R6LD5CPDGHDYALYWTCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FEHODDM5R6LD5CPDGHDYALYWTCE%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=2ef591f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FEHODDM5R6LD5CPDGHDYALYWTCE%2F&h=ce6a6754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/EHODDM5R6LD5CPDGHDYALYWTCE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國際法庭裁「九段線」違法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/034FLjt8cnLzdGUlNWp6nK3Hm44=/635x447/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IF6DDYRRFIAMZKFKIUXL7LWZ5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F034FLjt8cnLzdGUlNWp6nK3Hm44%3D%2F635x447%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIF6DDYRRFIAMZKFKIUXL7LWZ5U.gif&h=9e278c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國多年來於南海建立了多個設施。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中國向來與南海各國有領海爭議，菲律賓2013年向荷蘭海牙的仲裁法院提出「南海仲裁案」，指中國的「九段線」等領海主張違反《聯合國海洋法公約》（下稱《公約》），中方拒參與聽證。2016年仲裁結果傾向菲律賓，但中方繼續在南海擴張。杜特爾特2016年當選總統，一度擱置裁決，但近年態度轉強硬，令局勢有所變化。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美趨強硬「火藥桶」一觸即發<br />\n<br />\n九段線是中國於1953年主張，在中華民國蔣介石政府的十一段線基礎上，移除與越南相鄰的北部灣、東京灣兩線後成「九段線」，目的在於與越南修好。中方據此宣稱「九段。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n1999年，菲律賓以「戰艦船底漏水，不得已坐灘」為由，將戰艦停泊在中國宣稱擁有主權的南沙群島仁愛礁，至今仍未拖走。中國2013年底起陸續在南沙島礁吹沙填海，引起諸國不滿。2014年3月，菲律賓向海牙常設仲裁法院提交。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司/新華社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wqvpS78eLE2A-L9vwcPjIU-rKrY=/825x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G63QHGG4XRRLCNZVMX7S6DPCSI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwqvpS78eLE2A-L9vwcPjIU-rKrY%3D%2F825x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG63QHGG4XRRLCNZVMX7S6DPCSI.gif&h=47e08dd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"527bb738266160125e7ca515ac756bb0690c3fc6","tid":2109550,"uid":38777,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"支國唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68d4a83ccedfec726859ecb8f48c7a771c8d1fe","tid":2109550,"uid":37869,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"等睇廢紙一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998e83dcb28ed4347f55e16efb5f6405dff72997","tid":2109550,"uid":176313,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"527bb738266160125e7ca515ac756bb0690c3fc6","tid":2109550,"uid":38777,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"支國唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"美國師出有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20db3836b742583dcd5e31f929b8936af349726","tid":2109550,"uid":191926,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:06:02.000Z","msg":"劃到人地門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國民黨搞出來<br />\n共產黨繼承"},{"pid":"38ceacdc370bce8ad12240be6595bd7333a5b4ee","tid":2109550,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/